$ Oracle: Init parameter DDL_LOCK_TIMEOUT
@ ddl_lock_timeout

The value of `ddl_lock_timeout` specifies the timeout to restrict the time that → development/databases/Oracle/SQL/DDL statements wait for a → development/databases/Oracle/SQL/DML[DML] lock.

